            ""name"": ""Black Rock Nature Center"",
            ""description"": ""The Nature Center is open seven days a week from 8:00-11:00am and 12:00pm-4:00pm. It is closed from 11:00am - 12:00pm. Hours may vary depending on staff availability, especially in the summer.\n\nSummer Hours (June 1st):\nThe Nature Center is open Thursday through Sunday from 9am-4pm and closed Monday through Wednesday."",
