      {
        ""name"": ""Joshua Tree National Park Visitor Center"",
        ""parkCode"": ""jotr"",
        ""description"": ""The Joshua Tree National Park Visitor Center is located in downtown Twentynine Palms and features educational exhibits, a bookstore and giftshop, and visitor information."",
        ""url"": """",
        ""directionsInfo"": ""Heading east on Hwy 62 into the town of Twentynine Palms: Turn right onto Freedom Way, which may show up on your map as Yucca Ave. If you reach National Park Drive, you have gone too far. Heading west on Hwy 62 into the town of Twentynine Palms: Turn left onto Freedom Way (aka Yucca Ave). If you reach Tamarisk Ave you have gone too far. The Joshua Tree National Park Visitor Center is located next to Freedom Plaza, less than a block off of Hwy 62"",
        ""directionsUrl"": """",
