      ""name"": ""Yosemite Valley Welcome Center"",
      ""parkCode"": ""yose"",
      ""description"": ""The Yosemite Valley Welcome Center is the destination for visitor information in Yosemite Valley. Stop here before you begin your Yosemite adventure! The welcome center is located next to the Yosemite Village Parking and the Village Store in Yosemite Valley (Shuttle Stops 1 & 2.) Get help planning your visit with a ranger-staffed information desk, bookstore, and informational exhibits. Stop by to pick up free trail maps, junior ranger booklets, and more."",
