      ""name"": ""Alcatraz Island"",
      ""description"": ""Access to Alcatraz Island is via commercial ferry service. For ticket reservation and schedule call (415) 981-7625 or go to www.alcatrazcitycruises.com. The ferry schedule changes seasonally. Alcatraz is closed on Thanksgiving, Christmas and New Years Day. Once on the island you can stay up to the last ferry. \n\nBe aware that tickets sell out quickly and reservations are recommended. Tickets go on sale 90 days in advance."",
