    {
      ""title"": ""Entrance - Non-commercial Groups"",
      ""cost"": ""$20.00"",
      ""description"": ""Organized Non-Commercial Groups include church groups, college/school groups, scouts, service organizations, military, etc.\nVehicles with a capacity of 16 or less are charged the $20.00 vehicle permit fee. Vehicles with 17 or more seats will instead be charged the $10 per person individual rate for any passengers that are not free. The total fee charged for an Organized Non-Commercial Group will not exceed $100 per vehicle.""
    }
