      ""name"": ""Pinnacles Park Store"",
      ""parkCode"": ""pinn"",
      ""description"": ""Get your passport stamped and buy the official park souvenirs, all at the park store! Located in the Pinnacles campground, the store is open everyday, from 9:00 AM to 4:00 PM, including holidays. This fully stocked park store is operated by a private, non-profit organization called Western National Parks Association (WNPA). The park store carries a large variety of books, games, and souvenirs to help you learn more about the park and its resources."",
      ""url"": ""https://store.wnpa.org/park-stores/pinnacles-national-park.html"",
      ""directionsInfo"": ""Pinnacles Park Store is located off of Highway 25, thirty miles south of Hollister, California. Head two miles down the park road (East Entrance Road) and you will find the store on your left hand side, in the campground."",
